Add IOMMU_TYPE definition. In the mt8195, we have another IOMMU_TYPE:
infra iommu, also there will be another APU_IOMMU, thus, use 2bits for the
IOMMU_TYPE.

Signed-off-by: Yong Wu <yong.wu@mediatek.com>
